CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 16, 1947, pg. 16 reads: "Scenes From Night Of Stars - The Syria Mosque in Pittsburgh was packed to the rafters Monday night for the Frogs' "Night of Stars."...Upper panel shows part of the huge crowd with Earl Hines, Leslie Long, Billy Rowe, the orchestra and choir on the stage..."
TitMainTitle: Orchestra and choir on stage with Earl Hines, Leslie Long, Billy Rowe, in Syria Mosque with audience in foreground, for Night of Stars
